{"tid":776924,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"最強茶記炒蛋","createTime":"2018-08-12T13:27:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-12T17:49:10.000Z","uid":175988,"like":6,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ed55ef2e2651f3665a46ed8ca0753637072e1ece","tid":776924,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T13:27:06.000Z","msg":"<strong>四季常餐 @ 中環</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3br1XGu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F3br1XGu.jpg&h=f60a5dc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>炒蛋多士 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n炒蛋鮮嫩，蛋汁豐富，牛油香突出，生熟度啱啱好，質感輕盈軟滑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗返起仲有啲回味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n多士鬆軟帶牛奶香，外層焦脆而唔會過硬或者𠝹口，水準中上<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其他嘢食只係一般貨色，不過不失，唔食都無損失<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>結論: 點解炒蛋可以咁撚好食?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong>"},{"pid":"49a98d172d1abe972061d975d4c31a4cec2e6331","tid":776924,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T14:55:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d2dc777998ab7b10f0c66f3220e898e573499c0","tid":776924,"uid":157862,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T14:57:48.000Z","msg":"落雨仲叫炒蛋!?"},{"pid":"8e1f3bc11ef322811b69c3e0fe4d34f874c3055b","tid":776924,"uid":192327,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T14:58:16.000Z","msg":"咪L幫手吹啦 最多咪同華星澳牛差唔多<br />\n<br />\n搞到又勁多人去食 去打卡"},{"pid":"b49e8d9fa8bfd040d32f2be7663d8d1148840ab7","tid":776924,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8e1f3bc11ef322811b69c3e0fe4d34f874c3055b","tid":776924,"uid":192327,"l